<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-74-0397 </DOCNO><TEXT>Data on the sulfur dioxide emission in Hungary as well as the problemof deposition, further the principles of decreasing the emitted sulfurare dealt with. The historic review of the dynamics of decreasing theemission and results obtained up to the middle of the seventies are presented.A brief survey on the trends of flue gas desulfurization processes aswell as the tasks to be solved in the near future are listed.</TEXT></DOC>